13: I'm afraid I don't have that luxury!
17:
Barrier!
So long as this seal holds, you are 
powerless to stop me!
25:
Hack away at it all you like; the barrier 
isn't going anywhere, and neither are 
you!
29:
It is time, fox. We will send you back 
where you belong for once and for all, 
never to return again!
32:
N-never? But—
But what about Soushiro? And all the 
humans? ...I will never get to see them 
again?
36:
Inaho! Tell Soushiro what you told me! 
Hurry!
43:
I have never forgotten the day you 
saved me! I have always, always 
wanted to tell you how much it meant 
to me—how much YOU mean to me!
47:
Though my heart will always belong to 
my dear wife—may she rest in peace—
I am glad to have been of help.
49:
I knew you were the little fox I met so 
long ago. Thank you for coming back 
to visit me again, after all this time.
52:
You're... oh. B-but I too am glad to 
have met you again!
You too, girl whose name I know not!
59:
Stella! N-now that we know each 
other's names and everything, d-does 
that make us... friends?
67:
Ehehe... Ahaha!
You hear that diviner?! I have the 
power of friendship on my side, and 
friendship ALWAYS wins!
71:
Friendship... always wins? I could also 
say that justice always prevails. We 
shall see which is stronger.
75:
*yawn* Talk, talk, talk... Can we cut to 
the chase?
80:
You've been an absolute BORE, Izumi 
dear! Why fuss over what belongs in 
which world? They'll all be merged into 
one world anyways!
84:
But if you'd REALLY like the nine-tailed 
fox out of your hair, I'd be positively 
DELIGHTED to take her off your hands!
91:
Grand Diviner? Oh, you mean me? 
Goodness, I can't keep track of all the 
names I give boys.
105:
So many questions, so little time. 
Sorry darlings!
115: I knew you couldn't be trusted!
123:
My oh my! Looks like you shouldn't 
have trusted him either, Izumi!
127:
Don't get ahead of yourself, yokai brat. 
I'll be damned what the shogunate 
says!
129:
I'm not taking orders from the spawn 
of tengu! Of yokai!
138:
Oh DEAR! The people in this world are 
so VIOLENT! Ahaha, sounds like your 
kind of party, daemon darlings!
142:
Look out—these aren't your ordinary 
foes!
145: No need to hold back, then!
